    <item>
      <title>在中国困境中，资本和利润的上升幅度少于估计的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/capitaland-profit-rises-less-than-estimated-amid-china-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡的Capitaland Investment Ltd.报告了年度业绩，这些结果却遗失了估计，这是由于利率升高的环境及其对中国的敞口而受到的逆风，从而使私人资金等地区的收益越来越掩盖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/capitaland-profit-rises-less-than-estimated-amid-china-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 23:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
